1. User Role & Domain Selection
Allow users to specify their target job role and domain. This information will guide the bot in tailoring questions.

roles = ["Software Engineer", "Product Manager", "Data Analyst"]
domains = ["Frontend", "Backend", "Machine Learning", "System Design"]

def get_user_input():
    role = input(f"Select your role from {roles}: ")
    domain = input(f"Select your domain from {domains} (optional): ")
    return role, domain

